en_840954_0	To coincide with the 153rd proud anniversary celebration of the Sri Lanka Police, Nuwara Eliya Police Station organized a ‘Sharamadana’ drive around Gregory Lake on Friday (6).
en_840954_1	Tri service troops contributed to this event with much enthusiasm together with civil authorities of the area.
en_840954_2	Meanwhile, 21 troops including an Officer from 3 Sri Lanka Sinha Regiment assisted the project.
